at.easydiet.businessobjects

Packages that use at.easydiet.businessobjects
at.easydiet.businesslogic This is the root package of the A-Team business logic controllers. 
at.easydiet.businessobjects This package contains all business objects, used to get and set data. 
at.easydiet.domainlogic This package contains controllers, which are used in multiple use cases 
at.easydiet.teamc.view   
at.easydiet.validation This package contains validators, to ensure that everything is correct 
at.easydiet.view This package contains all background classes for the Pivot GUI 
at.easydiet.view.content This package contains all content renderers and bind mappings
